videos.description: D'Eriq King takes the pitch on the flea flicker and skies a 48-yard completion to Steven Dunbar who is tackled at the 1 yard line.
videos.headline: Houston gets to goal line with flea flicker

videos.description: Ed Oliver pounds in a 1-yard touchdown run to open the scoring in the Hawai'i Bowl.
videos.headline: Oliver puts Houston on the board

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion has his pass tipped and D'Juan Hines is there to grab it for the interception.
videos.headline: Houston's Hines gets tip drill INT

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion scores Fresno State's first touchdown of the game and evens the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: McMaryion scores on QB sneak

videos.description: Fresno State's head coach Jeff Tedford said his team needs to stop giving up big plays in the second half against Houston.
videos.headline: Fresno State looking to limit explosive plays

videos.description: D'Juan Hines forces a Marcus McMaryion fumble which is recovered by Terrell Williams for the Cougars.
videos.headline: Houston's Hines creates turnover

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion gives Fresno State the lead with a 6-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: McMaryion scores on the keeper

videos.description: Derek McLemore is unable to field the kickoff cleanly and Fresno State is able to recover with great field position.
videos.headline: Houston muffs kickoff

videos.description: After Jeremy Winchester blocks Jimmy Camacho's field goal attempt, the ball lands in Alexander Myres' arms, who takes it back for a Houston touchdown.
videos.headline: Houston returns FG block for TD

videos.description: Fresno State's Jamire Jordan dives to reel in the 37-yard pass from Marcus McMaryion.
videos.headline: Jordan lays out for great catch

videos.description: Linell Bonner reaches down and makes fantastic play to bring in the pass from D'Eriq King for a Houston first down.
videos.headline: Bonner makes incredible shoe-string catch

videos.description: Jaron Bryant picks off Houston's D'Eriq King and takes it back 44 yards for a Fresno State touchdown.
videos.headline: Fresno State's Bryant takes INT to the house

videos.description: Fresno State completes their 10-win season with a 33-27 win over Houston in the Hawai'i Bowl.
videos.headline: Fresno State wins the Hawai'i Bowl

videos.description: The Bulldogs score touchdowns in the second half off a blocked field goal and interception en route to a 33-27 victory against the Cougars.
videos.headline: Fresno State tops Houston in Hawai'i Bowl
